Project Title: File Sharing Platform

Project Overview --------------------------------------------------------------------------
The File Sharing Platform is a web-based application developed to enable users to transfer files from one device to another device through a website in a fast and secure manner. The platform allows users to upload and share files of up to 1 GB size without requiring physical storage devices like pen drives or hard disks.

The main purpose of this project is to provide a simple, efficient, and user-friendly solution for file transfer across different devices over the internet. Users can upload files on one device and access or download them on another device using a generated sharing link or unique access method.


Working of the System ----------------------------------------------------------------------

The system works in the following steps:

File Upload
The sender uploads a file to the platform through the website.
Storage & Processing
The file is temporarily stored on the server.
Link Generation / Access Method
A unique sharing link or access mechanism is generated.
File Sharing
The sender shares the link with another device/user.
File Download
The receiver opens the website and downloads the file securely.


